<p style="text-align: center;">招聘会现场。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200927/cabbc26d346e4b4da4c1ee2484244615.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
